Mobile Lending: members can now use an easy streamlined application for Auto loans, Rv loans, ATV/Motorcycle loans, Credit cards and Personal loans.

Balance Transfer Option: Members can now transfer a balance to an existing mountain America credit card or home equity line.

Skip a loan Payment: Members can skip a loan payment on an eligible loan.

Other Minor Bug Fixes

Introducing Apple Watch compatibility allowing our users to quickly check their account balances and view their most recent transactions on their watch while on the go.
Introducing Apple Watch compatibility allowing our users to quickly check their account balances and view their most recent transactions on their watch while on the go.

This update includes the introduction of biometric authentication! Our members get early access to this new technology. This includes eye recognition as well as fingerprint reading technology (must have a fingerprint reader on your device) for an extra layer of security on our app. You can choose to use one or the other or both!
